Sharpness

Boosts the power of slicing moves.

Affected Moves

The following moves are affected by this ability.

Name Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
Aerial Ace 20 60 — The user confounds the target with speed, then slashes. This attack never misses.
Air Cutter 25 60 95 The user launches razor-like wind to slash opposing Pokémon. Critical hits land more easily.
Air Slash 15 75 95 The user attacks with a blade of air that slices even the sky. It may make the target flinch.
Aqua Cutter 20 70 100 Expels pressurized water to cut the foe. It lands critical hits more easily.
Behemoth Blade 5 100 100 The user becomes a gigantic sword that deals double damage to energy-infused targets.
Bitter Blade 10 90 100 A bitter slash that restores the user's HP by half the damage taken by the target
Ceaseless Edge 15 65 90 The user slashes a shell blade, leaving shell splinters scatted on the foe's side.
Cross Poison 20 70 100 A slashing attack with a toxic blade that may also poison. Critical hits land more easily.
Cut 30 50 95 The target is cut with a scythe or claw.
Fire Lash 15 80 100 The user strikes the target with a burning lash. This also lowers the target's Defense stat.
Fury Cutter 20 40 95 The target is slashed with scythes or claws, intensifying on each successive hit.
Kowtow Cleave 10 85 — Slashes the target after their guard is down. It never misses.
Leaf Blade 15 90 100 The user handles a sharp leaf like a sword to cut its target. Critical hits land more easily.
Mighty Cleave 5 95 100 Cleaves the target with accumulated light, even if the target protects itself.
Night Slash 15 70 100 The user slashes the target the instant an opportunity arises. Critical hits land more easily.
Population Bomb 10 20 90 The user gather's a combo attack to hit between one and ten times.
Psyblade 15 80 100 Rend the foe with an ethereal blade. It's power is boosted by 50 percent in Electric Terrain.
Psycho Cut 20 70 100 The target is torn at by blades formed by psychic power. Critical hits land more easily.
Razor Leaf 25 55 95 Sharp-edged leaves are launched at opposing Pokémon. Critical hits land more easily.
Razor Shell 10 75 95 The user cuts its target with sharp shells. This may also lower its Defense stat.
Sacred Sword 15 90 100 The user attacks by slicing with a long horn, ignoring the target's stat changes.
Secret Sword 10 85 100 The user cuts with its long horn. The odd power contained inside does physical damage.
Silly Slash 15 70 100 The user slashes the target in an effervescent manner. Critical hits land more easily.
Slash 20 70 100 The target is attacked with a slash of claws or blades. Critical hits land more easily.
Solar Blade 10 125 100 The user fills a blade with the light's energy, attacking the target on the next turn.
Spark Blade 10 95 100 The user strikes with a blade that may paralyze. Critical hits land more easily.
Stone Axe 15 65 90 The user swings a stone axe, settings sharp rocks on the target's side.
Tachyon Cutter 10 50 — Launches particle blades to inflict damage. It hits twice, and never misses.
Triple Axel 10 20 90 A consecutive three-kick attack that becomes more powerful with each hit.
X-Scissor 15 80 100 The target is slashed at by scythes or claws crossed as if they were a pair of scissors.
